msgctxt "56_Concerned Car Owner"
msgid "There's been a chain of car break-ins around here lately."
msgstr "Últimamente, hay una oleada de robos de coches por aquí."

msgctxt "68_Imported Car Owner"
msgid "What? You can't be serious..."
msgstr "¿Qué? No puedes estar hablando en serio..."

msgctxt "80_Tanimura"
msgid "(Car break-ins, huh... Well, that sucks. I guess if I see one happening, I'll need to arrest whoever's responsible.)"
msgstr "(Robos de coches, eh... Eso apesta. Supongo que si lo veo,\\r\n"
"tendré que arrestar a quien sea el responsable.)"

